How to get your Gmail app password.

• Open myaccount.google.com
• Turn on 2 Step Verification
• Open App Passwords
• Create one for Mail
• Copy the 16 character password
• Paste it into SMTP_PASSWORD located at the .env file

How PHPMailer reads this.

In your PHP config file.

• Load .env using Dotenv
• Pass values into PHPMailer

Example values for you.

SMTP_USERNAME = your Gmail
SMTP_PASSWORD = the app password
MAIL_FROM_ADDRESS = same Gmail or your domain email

Now your system sends.

• Email to admins when complaint enters system
• Email to complainant when status changes

